    "en": {
      "title": "First Commonwealth medal from Isuru",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Weightlifter Isuru Kumara managed to win the first medal for Sri Lanka in this year's Commonwealth Games.",
        "He won the bronze medal in the men's 55 kg category in the tournament held in Birmingham.",
        "In this event, the gold medal was won by Mohammad Anik Bin Kasdan of Malaysia and the silver medal was won by Sank Sargar of India.",
        "Kumar lifted 105 kg in the snatch and 120 kg in the clean and jerk and scored a total of 225 points."
      ],
